metadata.name: #01 - FoundTheWei
metadata.description:
The EXPLORE4D series is a representation of my journey learning 3D art. I had no 3D experience prior to jumping into Cinema4D. All of these pieces were made within the second month of my "exploration" after I learned the basics. 

++1 
"FoundTheWei" encapsulates the personal growth, excitement, and expansiveness of the crypto space.
